{"tid":1474971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以唔好再估818遊行人數","createTime":"2019-08-15T10:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:56:29.000Z","uid":274371,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b3bcc5a33224494274fa2fa5b48549157d57112a","tid":1474971,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:37:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推爆818！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n但係，大家可唔可以唔好再估遊行人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時見到咩三百萬人、二百萬人上街，覺得咁唔係一個好嘅方向去號召大家。因為有時估完幾多人，如果遊行唔到數反而蝕咗大家士氣，所以都唔建議啲人去估數咩三百萬呀二百萬咁。<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都係為件事好，想號召更多人上街，但需要明白你講遊行預計有幾多人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係唔會號召到人架</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而可以宣揚「<strong>不是看見希望才努力，而是努力才可以看見希望</strong>」，有號召力得嚟又夠保守，唔洗玩估大小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要說：三百萬人818上街<br />\n試著說：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不是看見希望才努力，而是努力才可以看見希望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4e8d86881f20d15f659650fcfebcdf35431a9ab","tid":1474971,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"85a73943cecc328966a932ea012fbbc4580830c5","tid":1474971,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:39:20.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"55b3ff93a790dd3c114177217c78dafb59864f81","tid":1474971,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:40:20.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"2247c4be0aa33f243061cb9ff75a2e72743df6e7","tid":1474971,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"bea51319057f07325bad5f8d586a258bce7394cd","tid":1474971,"uid":274371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15